XP100/200/200 Hardware Configuration 
------------------------------------

The PLX9056, CDCE706/906 and NXP1520 EEPROMs on the XPs must be programmed at 
manufacturing time to their default configuration with the commands:

    maint loadplxeeprom -c N
    maint loadcdceeeprom -c N
    maint loadusbeeprom -c N

where 'N' is the channel number for the board.

The PLX9056 VPD must also be programmed at manufacture time. The command is:
     
    maint loadplxvpd -c N -s serial

where 'N' is the channel number  and 'serial' is the serial number for the 
board.
    
